00:40.092 --> 00:41.151
Well, they're crazy.

00:41.152 --> 00:43.041
Crazy.

00:43.042 --> 00:46.011
Anyway, I saw this cool
mesh shirt at fashion junkie,

00:46.012 --> 00:48.041
